---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services — RADIANX CAPITAL"
  description="Comprehensive wealth management services: investment management, financial planning, tax optimization, estate planning and more."
  currentPath="/services"
>



<!-- PAGE HEADER -->
<header class="ph">
  <div class="ph-atm"></div>
  <div class="ph-geo">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 600" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" fill="none">
      <g transform="translate(1200,300)">
        <g class="rot">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="250" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.025)" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M0,-250 A250,250 0 0,1 177,177" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.055)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </g>
        <g class="rotr">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="310" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.015)" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3,8"/>
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="ph-inner">
    <div class="sec-tag rv">What We Offer</div>
    <h1 class="ph-h rv">Wealth services<br>built for <em>complexity.</em></h1>
    <p class="ph-desc rv">
      No two clients share the same financial circumstances. Every service we provide is architected specifically around your situation — your assets, your goals, your timeline, your life.
    </p>
    
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════
  01 — INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT
══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="svc" id="investment">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <div class="svc-left">
      <div class="svc-left-top">
        <div class="svc-num rv">01 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 06</div>
        <div class="svc-sub rv">Core Service</div>
        <h2 class="svc-h rv">Investment<br><em>Management</em></h2>
        <p class="svc-body rv">
          At the center of every client relationship is a bespoke investment portfolio — constructed with precision, monitored continuously, and adapted as market conditions and personal circumstances evolve. We combine rigorous fundamental analysis with disciplined risk management to pursue long-term, risk-adjusted returns aligned with your specific objectives.
        </p>
        <p class="svc-body rv" style="margin-top:16px">
          Unlike firms that plug clients into predetermined model portfolios, we build each allocation from scratch. Your portfolio reflects your goals, your tax situation, your time horizon, and your risk tolerance — and nothing else.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-left-bot rv">
        <a href="/contact" class="svc-link">Discuss Your Portfolio →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-right rv">
      <div class="sf-list">
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Custom Portfolio Construction</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Each portfolio is built from the ground up around your individual objectives — never templated, never a product placement.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Active Risk Management</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Continuous monitoring of portfolio exposure, drawdown risk, correlation, and concentration — with proactive adjustment when conditions warrant.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Disciplined Rebalancing</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Systematic rebalancing to maintain target allocations and harvest tax efficiencies — executed with precision, not emotion.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Transparent Reporting</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Clear, regular reporting on portfolio performance, attribution, and positioning — so you always know exactly where you stand and why.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Multi-Asset Class Expertise</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Across equities, fixed income, alternatives, and cash — we manage the full spectrum of your investable assets with a single, coherent strategy.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-stat-row">
        <div class="svc-stat">
          <div class="svc-stat-n">$953<em>M+</em></div>
          <div class="svc-stat-l">Assets Under Management</div>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-stat">
          <div class="svc-stat-n">100<em>%</em></div>
          <div class="svc-stat-l">Fiduciary Standard</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════
  02 — FINANCIAL PLANNING
══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="svc alt" id="planning" style="background:var(--bg2)">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <div class="svc-right rv">
      <div class="sf-list">
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Comprehensive Financial Blueprint</div>
            <div class="sf-d">A full-scope plan covering income, expenses, savings, insurance, debt, education, retirement, and legacy — mapped to your life trajectory.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Cash Flow Optimization</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Detailed analysis and structuring of cash flows to maximize savings efficiency, liquidity, and capital deployment across time horizons.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Insurance & Protection Review</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Objective assessment of life, disability, long-term care, and liability coverage — identifying gaps and eliminating inefficiencies.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Education Funding Strategies</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Tax-advantaged structures for education funding — 529 plans, UGMA/UTMA accounts, and integrated family gifting strategies.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Ongoing Plan Maintenance</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Your financial plan is a living document. We revisit, update, and recalibrate it as your life evolves and circumstances change.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-stat-row">
        <div class="svc-stat">
          <div class="svc-stat-n">8<em>+ Yrs</em></div>
          <div class="svc-stat-l">Client Relationships</div>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-stat">
          <div class="svc-stat-n">360<em>°</em></div>
          <div class="svc-stat-l">Financial View</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-left">
      <div class="svc-left-top">
        <div class="svc-num rv">02 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 06</div>
        <div class="svc-sub rv">Foundational Service</div>
        <h2 class="svc-h rv">Financial<br><em>Planning</em></h2>
        <p class="svc-body rv">
          True financial security begins with a plan — not a product. We build a comprehensive, integrated financial blueprint that maps every dimension of your financial life: your income, your obligations, your protection needs, your aspirations, and your legacy.
        </p>
        <p class="svc-body rv" style="margin-top:16px">
          This is not a one-time exercise. Your financial plan is a living framework that we revisit, stress-test, and refine continuously — adapting to life events, tax law changes, and evolving goals with precision and clarity.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-left-bot rv">
        <a href="/contact" class="svc-link">Start Your Plan →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════
  03 — TAX OPTIMIZATION
══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="svc" id="tax">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <div class="svc-left">
      <div class="svc-left-top">
        <div class="svc-num rv">03 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 06</div>
        <div class="svc-sub rv">Strategic Service</div>
        <h2 class="svc-h rv">Tax<br><em>Optimization</em></h2>
        <p class="svc-body rv">
          Tax efficiency is not a feature we add to a portfolio — it is a discipline embedded into every investment decision we make. We integrate tax planning directly into portfolio management, ensuring that every allocation, rebalancing decision, and distribution is made with full awareness of its tax implications.
        </p>
        <p class="svc-body rv" style="margin-top:16px">
          Working in close coordination with your tax professionals, we identify and execute strategies that meaningfully reduce your annual tax burden — without compromising investment objectives or taking undue risk.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-left-bot rv">
        <a href="/contact" class="svc-link">Reduce Your Tax Burden →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-right rv">
      <div class="sf-list">
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Tax-Loss Harvesting</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Systematic identification and realization of investment losses to offset capital gains — executed continuously, not just at year-end.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Asset Location Optimization</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Strategic placement of asset classes across taxable, tax-deferred, and tax-exempt accounts to maximize overall after-tax returns.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Roth Conversion Planning</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Disciplined analysis of Roth conversion opportunities — identifying optimal timing and amounts given current and projected tax rates.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Charitable Giving Strategies</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Donor-advised funds, qualified charitable distributions, and appreciated asset gifting — structured to maximize both philanthropic impact and tax efficiency.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">CPA Coordination</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Seamless collaboration with your existing tax professionals to ensure investment decisions and tax planning are fully aligned throughout the year.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════
  04 — TRUST & ESTATE
══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="svc alt" id="estate" style="background:var(--bg2)">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <div class="svc-right rv">
      <div class="sf-list">
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Trust Structure Design</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Analysis and implementation of revocable and irrevocable trust structures — CRTs, GRATs, SLATs, IDGTs — tailored to your estate and tax situation.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Wealth Transfer Strategies</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Annual gift exclusion programs, intra-family loans, family limited partnerships, and other mechanisms to transfer wealth efficiently across generations.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Estate Tax Mitigation</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Proactive strategies to reduce federal and state estate tax exposure — modeled against current law and stress-tested against potential legislative changes.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Beneficiary Planning</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Comprehensive review and optimization of beneficiary designations across all accounts, policies, and retirement plans to ensure alignment with your estate plan.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Attorney Coordination</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Close collaboration with estate attorneys to ensure financial planning and legal documents are fully integrated and consistently maintained.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-left">
      <div class="svc-left-top">
        <div class="svc-num rv">04 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 06</div>
        <div class="svc-sub rv">Legacy Service</div>
        <h2 class="svc-h rv">Trust &amp;<br><em>Estate Planning</em></h2>
        <p class="svc-body rv">
          Wealth built over a lifetime should endure beyond it. We work with high-net-worth families to design and maintain the legal and financial structures that protect assets, minimize estate taxes, and ensure that wealth is transferred to the next generation with clarity and intention.
        </p>
        <p class="svc-body rv" style="margin-top:16px">
          Estate planning is not a static document — it is an ongoing discipline. We review your estate plan regularly, coordinate with your legal advisers, and adapt your strategy as tax laws, family circumstances, and asset values change.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-left-bot rv">
        <a href="/contact" class="svc-link">Protect Your Legacy →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════
  05 — RETIREMENT PLANNING
══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="svc" id="retirement">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <div class="svc-left">
      <div class="svc-left-top">
        <div class="svc-num rv">05 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 06</div>
        <div class="svc-sub rv">Income Service</div>
        <h2 class="svc-h rv">Retirement<br><em>Planning</em></h2>
        <p class="svc-body rv">
          Retirement is the most consequential financial transition most people face. We engineer it with the same rigor we apply to institutional mandates — building a sustainable income architecture that supports your lifestyle for life, regardless of market conditions or longevity.
        </p>
        <p class="svc-body rv" style="margin-top:16px">
          Our approach addresses both the accumulation and distribution phases — helping you build wealth efficiently before retirement, and draw it down intelligently after. We model Social Security timing, Required Minimum Distributions, healthcare costs, and inflation to construct a retirement income plan that holds up under stress.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-left-bot rv">
        <a href="/contact" class="svc-link">Plan Your Retirement →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-right rv">
      <div class="sf-list">
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Retirement Income Architecture</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Coordinated income streams from Social Security, pensions, portfolios, and annuities — sequenced to minimize taxes and maximize sustainability.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">401(k) &amp; IRA Optimization</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Contribution strategy, investment selection, and fee analysis across all employer-sponsored and individual retirement accounts.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Social Security Maximization</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Detailed modeling of claiming strategies — individual, spousal, and survivor benefits — to identify the lifetime-optimal filing approach.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">RMD Planning</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Proactive management of Required Minimum Distributions to minimize tax impact while integrating with broader estate and giving strategies.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Healthcare &amp; Longevity Modeling</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Comprehensive projection of healthcare costs, Medicare planning, and long-term care considerations — stress-tested for extended longevity scenarios.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════
  06 — ALTERNATIVE INVESTMENTS
══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="svc alt" id="alternatives" style="background:var(--bg2)">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <div class="svc-right rv">
      <div class="sf-list">
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Private Equity &amp; Credit</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Curated access to direct private equity investments, buyout funds, and private credit strategies with compelling risk-adjusted return profiles.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Real Assets</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Infrastructure, real estate, commodities, and natural resources — positioned as portfolio diversifiers with inflation-hedging characteristics.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Hedge Fund Strategies</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Access to liquid and semi-liquid alternative strategies — long/short equity, global macro, multi-strategy — for portfolio diversification and downside mitigation.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Structured Products</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Principal-protected notes, market-linked CDs, and other structured solutions designed to achieve specific risk/return profiles unavailable through conventional instruments.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sf">
          <div class="sf-dash">—</div>
          <div class="sf-text">
            <div class="sf-t">Rigorous Due Diligence</div>
            <div class="sf-d">Every alternative investment is subjected to thorough quantitative and qualitative analysis before being considered for any client portfolio.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-stat-row">
        <div class="svc-stat">
          <div class="svc-stat-n">Select<em> access</em></div>
          <div class="svc-stat-l">Qualified Investors Only</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-left">
      <div class="svc-left-top">
        <div class="svc-num rv">06 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 06</div>
        <div class="svc-sub rv">Advanced Service</div>
        <h2 class="svc-h rv">Alternative<br><em>Investments</em></h2>
        <p class="svc-body rv">
          Sophisticated investors know that traditional stocks and bonds are not the whole picture. Alternative investments — private equity, real assets, hedge strategies, and structured products — offer return streams, diversification benefits, and inflation protection that conventional markets cannot provide.
        </p>
        <p class="svc-body rv" style="margin-top:16px">
          We provide qualified clients with carefully vetted access to alternative investment opportunities typically reserved for large institutions. Every opportunity is rigorously analyzed before it is presented, and every allocation is sized appropriately within the context of your broader financial plan.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-left-bot rv">
        <a href="/contact" class="svc-link">Explore Alternatives →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ COMPARISON ═══ -->
<section class="compare">
  <div class="compare-inner">
    <div class="sec-tag rv">Why Choose Us</div>
    <h2 class="sec-h rv" style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(34px,3.5vw,52px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-.3px;margin-bottom:0">Fiduciary advice<br><em>vs.</em> the alternative</h2>
    <div class="compare-table rv">
      <div class="ct-head">
        <div class="ct-hc">Feature</div>
        <div class="ct-hc hl">RADIANX</div>
        <div class="ct-hc">Typical Broker</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-row">
        <div class="ct-c feature">Legally required to act in your interest</div>
        <div class="ct-c yes"><div class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 4l2 2 3-3" stroke="rgba(122,150,168,.9)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Always</div>
        <div class="ct-c no"><div class="cross"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M2 2l4 4M6 2L2 6" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>No</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-row">
        <div class="ct-c feature">Fee-only, no commissions</div>
        <div class="ct-c yes"><div class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 4l2 2 3-3" stroke="rgba(122,150,168,.9)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Always</div>
        <div class="ct-c no"><div class="cross"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M2 2l4 4M6 2L2 6" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Rarely</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-row">
        <div class="ct-c feature">Fully customized portfolios</div>
        <div class="ct-c yes"><div class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 4l2 2 3-3" stroke="rgba(122,150,168,.9)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Always</div>
        <div class="ct-c no"><div class="cross"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M2 2l4 4M6 2L2 6" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Model-based</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-row">
        <div class="ct-c feature">Integrated tax planning</div>
        <div class="ct-c yes"><div class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 4l2 2 3-3" stroke="rgba(122,150,168,.9)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Included</div>
        <div class="ct-c no"><div class="cross"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M2 2l4 4M6 2L2 6" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Extra cost</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-row">
        <div class="ct-c feature">SEC registered &amp; regulated</div>
        <div class="ct-c yes"><div class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 4l2 2 3-3" stroke="rgba(122,150,168,.9)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Yes</div>
        <div class="ct-c no"><div class="cross"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M2 2l4 4M6 2L2 6" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Varies</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-row">
        <div class="ct-c feature">Transparent, disclosed fees</div>
        <div class="ct-c yes"><div class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 4l2 2 3-3" stroke="rgba(122,150,168,.9)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Always</div>
        <div class="ct-c no"><div class="cross"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><path d="M2 2l4 4M6 2L2 6" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>Often hidden</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ PROCESS ═══ -->
<section class="process">
  <div class="sec-tag rv">How It Works</div>
  <h2 rv style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(34px,3.5vw,52px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-.3px;margin-bottom:0" class="rv">From first call to<br><em>ongoing partnership</em></h2>
  <div class="process-grid">
    <div class="pg rv">
      <div class="pg-line"></div>
      <div class="pg-n">01 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 04</div>
